Oh no, I'm getting excited again!
Just let me know when you are coming.
My mom has a summer apt on 11th street that I have access to all
winter long. She doesn't come up til May, so it's empty. We just
had the electric and water turned on last week so my brother and
family could stay there over Easter. So there will be a bathroom
and refrigerator AND shower for anyone that needs it.
check the weather and make the plans!
Joanna
